description:
Today Parisian Vibe and Lea are strolling the streets of Paris to show you our 5 best coffee shops in Paris. These authentic cafes were handpicked by the team and Lea for you to discover whether you are visiting or living in Paris. Our main criteria was (of course) good coffee and cool company. It is not just another “cup of coffee”, each place has something special about it. Go get your cup of coffee and let us know what you think.
*NOTE: FRENCH SUBTITLES AVAILABLE*
___________
*ADDRESSES OF THE COFFEE SHOPS:*

• Coffee Place No 1 - KB Coffee Roasters:
   53 Av. Trudaine, 75009 Paris
   Follow  on instagram ►► https://instagram.com/kbcoffeeroastersparis

• Coffee Place No 2 - Blackbird Coffee:
   54 Rue des Trois Frères, 75018 Paris
   Follow  on instagram ►► https://instagram.com/blackbirdcoffee.official

• Coffee Place No 3 - The Beans on Fire:
   61 Rue des Trois Frères, 75018 Paris
   Follow  on instagram ►► https://instagram.com/thebeansonfire

• Coffee Place No 4 - Noir Coffee Shop:
   120 Bd Haussmann, 75008 Paris
    Follow  on instagram ►► https://instagram.com/noir_coffeeshop

• Coffee Place No 5 - Café Kitsuné:
   208 Rue de Rivoli, 75001 Paris
   Follow  on instagram ►► https://instagram.com/cafekitsune
